items.shortDescription: Keep your pencils sharp and ready with the help of this X-ACTO Model 1900 Desktop Electric Pencil Sharpener. It can sharpen your pencil quickly and easily. The Singing Machine CDG Karaoke System SML385 includes a built-in speaker, wired microphone, AC adapter, RCA cables, sampler disc and instruction manual.</p>

items.name: Garmin Forerunner 10 Watch, ( Assorted Colors)
items.shortDescription: The stylish Garmin Forerunner 10 Watch tracks your distance, pace and calories, allowing you to optimize your workout. With a high-sensitivity GPS receiver, this Garmin 10 Watch, in Pink/White, records your position and can help you to identify your personal records. Featuring a virtual pacer, this Garmin Forerunner Watch compares current pace to target run/walk feature, allowing you to keep on track. This Garmin Forerunner 10 Watch also features auto lap and auto pause. You can visit Garmin Connect to store and share workouts. The Garmin Forerunner 10 is water resistant up to 50 meters and has an automatic time zone feature. The built-in rechargeable lithium-ion battery in this watch can last up to five hours in training mode or up to five weeks in power save mode.
